{"tid":93503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢10秒炸平19幢樓　將建707米全市最高樓","createTime":"2017-01-24T13:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T06:18:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b9abaa8f5913124cc3a66e2ec9445b88d5e7b4c","tid":93503,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170122/photo/bkncn-20170122091254223-0122_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170122104042\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170122%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170122091254223-0122_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170122104042&h=d4531843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湖北武漢計劃興建一座高達707米的全市第一高樓，昨晚在相關區域進行了一次全國最大建築群爆破，當局在現場共設置逾12萬個鑽炮口，使用5噸炸藥，在隆隆爆破聲中，19幢樓順序倒下，整個過程僅用了約10秒。 <br />\n<br />\n該次爆破的19幢樓房分別高7至12層，總建築面積約15萬平方米，位處解放大道頭道街至二七路段的繁華鬧市，四周還有多個住宅小區、學校、行人天橋，地下亦埋有高壓電纜、自來水及天然氣管道。 <br />\n<br />\n這次已是該區域第三次爆破拆除，截至目前已爆破拆除32幢樓。爆破完成後，該區未來將興建一座707米的高樓、一條過江隧道、一個地下中心城市，規劃面積288公頃，未來很可能成為漢口新中心。"},{"pid":"74872cbf6e1fef49ac40be6898271e27d8d72cf6","tid":93503,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202ffc4d66bf12b76007c2945bf6b44cd56ff8e5","tid":93503,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:02:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10cb50bd984defb3e36e5b7c07a9632c1be953e3","tid":93503,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"其實呢個係老衲練成葵花寶典嘅場面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f6a449a0e55fb7890ba9758014461d3f893c6f","tid":93503,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:13:35.000Z","msg":"創造就業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3cf952fdb5007332a335eb36caeb2e0cbadca8","tid":93503,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"